{"type":"message","id":"9253e674","parentId":"3a3de114","timestamp":"2026-03-19T01:14:30.905Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:cfd2966c-5e50-4153-ac26-a51b644dbe4a 每日AI科技早报] 请帮我搜索今日AI科技领域的热点新闻和重要资讯，整理成简洁清晰的早报内容发给用户。搜索关键词：AI、人工智能、大模型、OpenAI、ChatGPT、DeepSeek等。\n\n要求：\n1. 标题+简要说明\n2. 控制在5-10条以内\n3. 简洁清晰\n4. 早上9点发送，所以搜索的是最新动态\nCurrent time: Thursday, March 19th, 2026 — 9:14 AM (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-03-19 01:14 UTC\n\nReturn your summary as plain text; it will be delivered automatically. If the task explicitly calls for messaging a specific external recipient, note who/where it should go instead of sending it yourself."}],"timestamp":1773882870896}}
{"type":"message","id":"7be56590","parentId":"9253e674","timestamp":"2026-03-19T01:14:52.087Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户要求我搜索今日AI科技领域的热点新闻和重要资讯，整理成简洁清晰的早报内容。搜索关键词包括AI、人工智能、大模型、OpenAI、ChatGPT、DeepSeek等。\n\n现在是2026年3月19日早上9点14分，需要搜索最新的AI科技资讯。\n\n我需要先使用搜索工具来获取最新的AI新闻。让我使用web-search技能来搜索。","thinkingSignature":"fb3c638e51ab8d737992000ceb8c6ba833a856269627c7fcf8340e2121c7d876"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_koxs4sjd9063_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s \"https://newsapi.org/v2/top-headlines?category=technology&language=en&apiKey=demo\" 2>/dev/null | head -100 || echo \"需要使用搜索工具\"","timeout":10}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":52,"output":159,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":32781,"totalTokens":32992,"cost":{"input":0.0000156,"output":0.0001908,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0.00393372,"total":0.00414012}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773882870900}}
