s/wira01035?source=Site_0_JNY_WIR_DESKTOP_NAV_ROLLOVER_0_US_ACQ_NLI_QUICK_PAY_GENERIC_ZZ_PANELA)\n\n[Sign In](http://wired.com/auth/initiate?redirectURL=%2Ftag%2Fartificial-intelligence%2F&source=VERSO_NAVIGATION)\n\n# artificial intelligence\n\n![Image 2: Why Walmart and OpenAI Are Shaking Up Their Agentic Shopping Deal](https://media.wired.com/photos/69b9c55f4318d2003e7286fe/3:2/w_1280%2Cc_limit/business_walmart_openai_shopping_chatbot.jpg)\n\nBusiness\n\n[### Why Walmart and OpenAI Are Shaking Up Their Agentic Shopping Deal](http://wired.com/story/ai-lab-walmart-openai-shaking-up-agentic-shopping-deal/)\n\nBy Paresh Dave\n\n![Image 3: Justice Department Says Anthropic Can’t Be Trusted With Warfighting Systems](https://media.wired.com/photos/69b9b3b8a5694fbea42e1cf8/3:2/w_1280%2Cc_limit/buisness_DOD_Anthropic_GettyImages-2265262796.jpg)\n\nBusiness\n\n[### Justice Department Says Anthropic Can’t Be Trusted With Warfighting Systems](http://wired.com/story/department-of-defense-responds-to-anthropic-lawsuit/)\n\nBy Paresh Dave\n\n![Image 4: How Invisalign Became the World’s Biggest User of 3D Printers](https://media.wired.com/photos/69a6021b9601628729405650/3:2/w_1280%2Cc_limit/CEO%2520Joe%2520Hogan.jpg)\n\nBusiness\n\n[### How Invisalign Became the World’s Biggest User of 3D Printers](http://wired.com/story/how-invisalign-became-the-worlds-biggest-3d-printing-company/)\n\nBy Paresh Dave\n\n![Image 5: Sears Exposed AI Chatbot Phone Calls and Text Chats to Anyone on the Web](https://media.wired.com/photos/69b868c66b808f7f94b9eeb5/3:2/w_1280%2Cc_limit/security_searsleak_Getty.jpg)\n\nSecurity\n\n[### Sears Exposed AI Chatbot Phone Calls and Text Chats to Anyone on the Web](http://wired.com/story/sears-exposed-ai-chatbot-phone-calls-and-text-chats-to-anyone-on-the-web/)\n\nBy Lily Hay Newman and Matt Burgess\n\n![Image 6: ‘100 Video Calls Per Day’: Models Are Applying to Be the Face of AI Scams](https://media.wired.com/photos/699f5d34a7cb1833c2431617/3:2/w_1280%2Cc_lim